Service Agreement – Confidential

This Service Agreement is made effective from 15/02/2026 between KBS Technologies and SAI Logistics.

The agreement outlines compliance requirements, data protection policies, and contractual obligations. Both parties agree to maintain confidentiality and adhere to applicable legal regulations.

The total contract value is ₹750000 payable in three installments. The first payment of ₹250000 was made on 20/02/2026.

Any breach of agreement will result in legal action as per corporate compliance policies. This agreement shall remain valid for a period of 12 months from the date of signing.

Both parties confirm acceptance of the terms and conditions mentioned above.